## ♿ Accessibility Requirements

### Dark Theme Considerations
- **Text contrast**: Minimum 4.5:1 ratio (#f5f5f5 on #0a0a0a = 17:1 ✓)
- **Interactive elements**: Minimum 3:1 ratio
- **Focus indicators**: White ring (#ffffff) with 2px offset
- **Avoid pure black/white**: Use near-black/near-white for reduced eye strain

### Keyboard Navigation
- All interactive elements tabbable
- Visible focus indicators (white ring on dark)
- Skip to main content link
- Logical tab order
- ESC to close modals/panels

### Screen Readers
- Semantic HTML (`<nav>`, `<main>`, `<article>`)
- ARIA labels where needed
- Alt text for all images
- Descriptive link text
- Proper heading hierarchy (h1 → h2 → h3)

